# 📋 COMPONENT CHECKLIST

## Before Committing Any Component

### TypeScript
- [ ] No `any` types (use proper interfaces)
- [ ] All props have types
- [ ] Return type is explicit or inferred correctly
- [ ] Exported interfaces for reusable components

### Carbon Compliance
- [ ] Using Carbon components (not custom HTML)
- [ ] Using Carbon spacing tokens
- [ ] Using Carbon color tokens
- [ ] Icons from `@carbon/icons-react`

### States
- [ ] Loading state implemented
- [ ] Error state implemented
- [ ] Empty state implemented
- [ ] Disabled state implemented
- [ ] Hover state styled
- [ ] Focus state visible

### Accessibility
- [ ] Keyboard navigation works
- [ ] Focus management correct
- [ ] ARIA labels on icon buttons
- [ ] Semantic HTML used
- [ ] Color contrast meets WCAG AA

### UX Polish
- [ ] Smooth transitions (200ms)
- [ ] Feedback for every action
- [ ] Clear error messages
- [ ] Helpful empty states
- [ ] Consistent spacing

### Performance
- [ ] No unnecessary re-renders
- [ ] Expensive operations memoized
- [ ] Event handlers debounced/throttled
- [ ] Images optimized

